rows.label: bf09300100_0020
rows.name: Blades become Divine Beasts when their time is up...

rows.label: bf09300100_0030
rows.name: And those Divine Beasts give birth to many new Blades.

rows.label: bf09300100_0040
rows.name: All while forming the world beneath our feet.

rows.label: bf09300100_0050
rows.name: It's amazing.

rows.label: bf09300100_0052
rows.name: It's enough to make me envious.

rows.label: bf09300100_0060
rows.name: Envious...of us?

rows.label: bf09300100_0070
rows.name: So I'd like to ask God.

rows.label: bf09300100_0080
rows.name: Homura, Hikari, all of you...

rows.label: bf09300100_0090
rows.name: Why did he create all these incredible people?

rows.label: bf09300100_0100
rows.name: Actually, I think I might already know the answer.

rows.label: bf09300100_0110
rows.name: So, I want to go see if I'm correct.

rows.label: bf09300100_0120
rows.name: To check your answer?

rows.label: bf09300100_0130
rows.name: Yeah.

rows.label: bf09300100_0140
rows.name: You...believe you know the reason we exist?

rows.label: bf09300100_0150
rows.name: Hrk-!

rows.label: bf09300100_0160
rows.name: Shin!

rows.label: bf09300100_0170
rows.name: Yoshitsune! Benkei!

rows.label: bf09300100_0180
rows.name: Benkei...

rows.label: bf09300100_0190
rows.name: I won't let you kill Shin.

rows.label: bf09300100_0200
rows.name: Stand down, Benkei.

rows.label: bf09300100_0210
rows.name: But-!

rows.label: bf09300100_0220
rows.name:
It is over for us now.
There is nothing more.

rows.label: bf09300100_0230
rows.name: We've done all that we have to.

rows.label: bf09300100_0240
rows.name: Shin...

rows.label: bf09300100_0250
rows.name: Nia...

rows.label: bf09300100_0260
rows.name: M-me?

rows.label: bf09300100_0270
rows.name: Your power... Can you use it on Shin...?

rows.label: bf09300100_0280
rows.name:
Well, sure...
It'll only be a temporary measure, but...

rows.label: bf09300100_0290
rows.name: Don't expect any thanks.

rows.label: bf09300100_0310
rows.name:
We'll go back first
and prep Shin for treatment.

rows.label: bf09300100_0320
rows.name: Yoshitsune! Make yourself useful.

rows.label: bf09300100_0330
rows.name: Yeah, yeah. I got 'im.

rows.label: bf09300100_0332
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]DISTRESS

rows.label: bf09300100_0335
rows.name: Benkei!!!

rows.label: bf09300100_0340
rows.name: You will climb no further...

rows.label: bf09300100_0350
rows.name: Wh-! Marveni? Here?!

rows.label: bf09300100_0360
rows.name: And...why does he look like that?!

rows.label: bf09300100_0370
rows.name:
If God did send Blades down to this world...
it was for my sake.

rows.label: bf09300100_0380
rows.name:
To find and raise cores containing more
powerful, wondrous, unparalleled data...

rows.label: bf09300100_0390
rows.name: That is why I created the cleansing procedure.

rows.label: bf09300100_0400
rows.name: Behold the culmination of my work!

rows.label: bf09300100_0410
rows.name: You lunatic...

rows.label: bf09300100_0420
rows.name: He took the cores from all those Blades...

rows.label: bf09300100_0430
rows.name: So that was the reason for the cleansing...

rows.label: bf09300100_0440
rows.name: I am an agent of God's will

rows.label: bf09300100_0450
rows.name: What is he saying?

rows.label: bf09300100_0460
rows.name: Delusions of grandeur...

rows.label: bf09300100_0470
rows.name: You can't just decide stuff like that, dude!

rows.label: bf09300100_0480
rows.name: You're out of your damned mind!

rows.label: bf09300100_0490
rows.name:
It is no delusion!
Have you forgotten the Holy Grail's power?

rows.label: bf09300100_0500
rows.name: That power...

rows.label: bf09300100_0510
rows.name:
Is it not the Holy Grail's power to erase
worthless things from existence?!

rows.label: bf09300100_0520
rows.name: Is that not God's very will?!

rows.label: bf09300100_0530
rows.name: Homura and Hikari aren't like that!

rows.label: bf09300100_0540
rows.name: ...I just realized.

rows.label: bf09300100_0550
rows.name:
I know why Metsu is so intent
on scouring the world...

rows.label: bf09300100_0560
rows.name: It's you, Marveni.

rows.label: bf09300100_0570
rows.name: Metsu has become tainted by your influence...

rows.label: bf09300100_0580
rows.name:
So what if he has?
What's the problem?

rows.label: bf09300100_0590
rows.name: You've had your little trip around Alst...

rows.label: bf09300100_0600
rows.name: You witnessed the state of Mors!

rows.label: bf09300100_0610
rows.name:
Mankind will never change,
no matter how many millennia pass!
